  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.event.ListSelectionListener, javax.swing.ListCellRenderer<Location>

     class SearchForLocationPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements javax.swing.ListCellRenderer<Location>, javax.swing.event.ListSelectionListener
    A SearchForLocationPanel extends JPanel. A SearchForLocationPanel implements the ListCellRenderer interface, to help build the JList A SearchForLocationPanel implements ListSelectionListener. A SearchForLocationPanel allows the user to set the Location for the OwmClient. Changing location will update the ScrollableGui with the weather. Saving a location will cause the ConfigurationManager to write a Configuration to file. App manages all of these processes through the SearchForLocationPanel.
    Author:
    Andrew Bloch-Hansen, Saquib Mian
    See Also:
